*item cfiles clm_file_contents
'A weather file holds hourly values for diffuse horizontal'
'solar irradiance (W/m^2), dry bulb temperature (tenths C),'
'direct normal or global horizontal solar irradiance (W/m^2),'
'wind speed (tenths m/s), wind direction (deg from North -'
'clockwise positive), and relative humidity (%). The normal'
'location is /usr/esru/esp-r/climate.'
